In order to build and run this application, jteigen's ScalaTest plugin for Maven is needed. The plugin can be found here:

    http://github.com/teigen/maven-scalatest-plugin

Clone the repository and then run

    mvn clean install

Then run the following commands:

    mvn scala:run -Dlauncher=backendServer (to run the backend server)
    mvn jetty:run (to run the frontend application)

Before testing the application, start the CouchDB server.